ation tag through the public BCFIPS JCA provider API, reaching:\n  - `ClassUtil.lookup(...)`\n  - `ClassUtil.findExceptionConstructor(...)`\n  - `ClassUtil.throwBadTagException(...)`\n- Updated existing placeholder test class to be public:\n  - `tests/src/org.bouncycastle/bc-fips/2.1.2/src/test/java/org_bouncycastle/bc_fips/Bc_fipsTest.java`\n\nPer instruction, I did not run compilation or tests.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0543505c87b61770016a3f72f40c3081979d4b339968e0ddda\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1292, "output": 1212, "cacheRead": 35328, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 37832, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782543074071, "responseId": "resp_0543505c87b61770016a3f72e287c881978ddeb61b48a2e8a1"}, "toolResults": []}
