[thinking] 
[thinking] It looks like I’m wondering about tests in the subproject and how they can be structured. I’m considering if only package-private tests can be run by JUnit 5, and whether we need to include our new test file in the test jar. There’s the idea of calling ClassUtil through a Java public wrapper, but I need to figure out how to keep tests outside library packages. I also need to consider using method handles instead of direct reflection, although that might not be easy.
[thinking] 
