[thinking] 
[thinking] I’m grappling with whether to avoid certain approaches unless absolutely necessary. This is my third attempt at creating a test helper. I need to remember to keep tests outside of library packages to prevent accessing package-private code directly. I’m thinking about whether the GcmSpecUtil static initialization might be getting triggered during build time rather than runtime. It seems the tests won't influence static initialization since that happens at build time. Maybe I should look into using system properties or reports generated during analysis for insights.
